00:01:33.410 --> 00:01:34.410
Cloverfield

00:01:34.410 --> 00:01:39.759
A good mystery often draws people into the
theater, and producer J.J. Abrams, writer

00:01:39.759 --> 00:01:44.920
Drew Goddard and director Matt Reeves used
a veil of mystery and a hint of epic peril

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:48.940
