00:02:16.990 --> 00:02:19.340
Terminator Salvation

00:02:19.340 --> 00:02:23.309
Terminator Salvation was scrutinized from
the moment it went into production, and the

00:02:23.309 --> 00:02:27.909
stories that surround it are still talked
about today (that Christian Bale on-set rant

00:02:27.909 --> 00:02:39.000
