futuristic world, thrilling action and intriguing

00:02:50.950 --> 00:02:55.889
sci-fi concepts, this trailer did everything
right in selling a new vision of the Terminator

00:02:55.889 --> 00:03:00.580
franchise. When Terminator Salvation finally
hit theatres, it quickly became clear that

00:03:00.580 --> 00:03:05.279
the studio had loaded all of the best moments
from the movie into the trailer. The full-length

00:03:05.279 --> 00:03:10.319
film was pretty forgettable - and ironically,
the trailer, for all its epicness, spoils

00:03:10.319 --> 00:03:18.450
what is arguably the best twist in the movie.
So much hype, for so little payoff.

00:03:18.450 --> 00:03:21.249
